data.description: Exquisite Remodeled home with modern upgrades and new roof /gutter system in the highly sought after White Rock Estates. Welcome to your perfect oasis in the desirable Carothers Neighborhood. This meticulously remodeled home showcases a brand new roof and gutters that add to the striking curb appeal, while ensuring long-lasting durability and protection. Step inside and be captivated by the modern luxury and attention to detail throughout. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's  dream, featuring all new stainless appliances, including a farm sink that perfectly compliments the space. Rest easy knowing that routine maintenance has been diligently performed on all appliances (ie. HVAC) guaranteeing seamless functionality for years to come. All cabinetry has been skillfully sanded down and waxed exuding a rustic elegance that adds character to the space. As you explore, you'll appreciate the warm ambiance created by the new light fixtures and outdoor lighting. These enhancements not only add visual appeal but also offer a delightful setting for outdoor entertaining and relaxation. Inside the entire home is bathed in luminous light from new bulbs, creating an inviting and welcoming atmosphere. Stay comfortable and worry-free with the installation of a new water heater that ensures  efficiency and reliability. The bathrooms have been thoughtfully updated with sophisticated fixtures and finishes that elevate the homes overall design. A fresh coat of paint throughout breathes new life into the interior, setting the stage for your personal style to shine. the tile, extended throughout all bedrooms and living room ensures cohesive and easy to maintain space that's perfect for both daily living and entertaining. With meticulous attention to detail, this home seamlessly combines modern amenities with classic charm. Don't miss your chance to make this exceptional remodeled property with a new roof and gutter system in the Carothers neighborhood your forever haven. Schedule now.
